author: wn.com
title: Tea Party wave that lifted Republicans threatens to engulf them
text: WASHINGTON (Reuters) - In Washington, Republicans are rudderless after their candidate to lead the House of Representatives drops out. On the campaign trail, seasoned conservatives struggle in the presidential race while a reality TV star alienates the nation's fastest-growing slice of the electorate.
